INSTALL BurpSuite community edition
Go to firefox and add extension foxyproxy
Enter ip address : 127.0.0.1 and port as 8080
Now go to settings in firefox and search xy settings
Click on manual configuration and enter 127.0.0.1 and port as 8080 in http proxy and also use it for https and click on ok
Go to http://burp and download ca certificate
Go to certificate settings in firefox and import this downloaded certificate
In burpsuite community edition , open proxy and click on intercept on
Now open http://testphp.vulnweb.com and refresh page , u will find its data in burpsuite
